parameters:
\n<Deorc>"Damn it, stop dawdling! How long does it take to destroy a
single town?!"

\n<Deorc>"...Everything was going so smoothly until now. What the
hell happened...?"

\n<Deorc>"This is such a pain... Maybe it's a good opportunity to try
that thing...?"

\n<Deorc>"Ah?... What's this all about? I thought it was strange that
the monsters started getting beaten all of a sudden, so it
was your doing, huh?"

\n<Deorc>"You've done well to get this far. Weren't you captured by
those guys?"
\n<Roselitte>"I have no intention of making idle chit-chat."

\n<Roselitte>"I won't let you do as you please any longer. Prepare
yourself."

\n<Deorc>"Heh. You always talk big. If you hadn't lost that time,
none of this would have happened."

\n<Roselitte>"Why attack Annabern? Isn't your goal the imperial
mainland?"

\n<Deorc>"The imperial mainland?... Heh. Well, attacking there isn't
a bad idea either."

\n<Deorc>"You're an idiot if you don't know. I'll crush anything I
don't like, anything that's in my way. That's all there is
to it."
Deorc took out a "book" from his pocket.
\n<Deorc>"Hey, Roselitte. This thing is really amazing..."

\n<Deorc>"This is the god that will grant my wishes. If I'm receiving
favors from a god--"
\n<Deorc>"--then I gotta give my thanks, right?!"

parameters.name: 猛獣の鳴き声（低いうなり声）

parameters:
\n<Deorc>"Roselitte of the Twelve Royal Knights! You're the perfect
offering for the god!"

\n<Lyric>"Whoa... Seriously... Roselitte, this one's the real deal! A
real Grim Reaper!"

\n<Lyric>"It wouldn't be strange if this one could use monster taming
magic itself! It's on a different level from other monsters!
We have no chance if we fight it head-on!"
\n<Roselitte>"This is bad...--Valam soldiers! Everyone, to the front!"

\n<Soldiers>"Aaaaaahhhhh!! It's the Grim Reaper!!" "Help...! Someone
help us!!" "Eeeeeeek!? Run awayyyyyy!!"
\n<Roselitte>"What...!? Where are you going, come back here!"

parameters.name: 猛獣の鳴き声（低いうなり声）

parameters: \n<Ameria>"Ah... Ahh... No, this is... I'm going to be killed..."

\n<Lyric>"What are you saying?! There's no way you can win alone! Are
you planning to die?!"

\n<Roselitte>"Take Ameria to a safe place! And report this to Annabelle!
If we don't, all the villagers will be slaughtered!"

\n<Roselitte>"You're the only one I can rely on! I'll buy time, so
hurry!"
\n<Roselitte>"If you don't, you'll be killed as well!"

\n<Deorc>"You think we'll let you escape?! Monsters, chase after
those who fled!"
